    "paidOnly": "Paid only, starting from $30/month. No free tier.",
    "purposeBuilt": "Purpose-built & flexible",
    "FIX SpaceDescription": "The FIX Space: Seven pre-configured databases ready on day one — journal, routines, strategies.",
